            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flow-arrow">‚Üí</div>
          <div class="flow-step">
            <div class="flow-icon">üî¨</div>
            <h3 class="flow-title">Step 3: Specific Mold Testing</h3>
            <p class="flow-description">
              Blood, urine, or skin tests are ordered to find evidence of mold
              allergy or mycotoxins.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

